STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Isaiah Ramon HENDERSON, Defendant-Appellant. No. 17-1388 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed December 5, 2018

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

Isaiah Henderson appeals his convictions for two counts of delivery of crack cocaine and one count of interference with official acts inflicting bodily injury. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
